‚ú® HOSTING FEATURES (ALL PLANS)
==============================

SPEED

* Optimized WordPress environment
* Smart caching & CDN-ready setup
* Fast loading across devices

SECURITY

* Real-time monitoring
* Regular backups & Auto-updates.
* Firewall protection

DOMAINS

* Use your own domain (pointing included)
* Hosting plans cover server infrastructure only.
* The cost of registering a new custom domain (e.g., .com, .ng) is separate and varies by extension.
* We can register a domain for you during setup (invoiced separately), or you can connect a domain you already own for free.
* Free edgely.me subdomains are available for you to get online at no cost throughout one year.

MIGRATION

* Full site migration handled by us
* Zero downtime
* Included in all plans

SUPPORT

* Hybrid Support System: We use a fluid combination of Email Tickets and WhatsApp to keep you connected on your preferred channel.
* Response Times: Launch (Standard), Grow & Pro (Priority/Dedicated Speed).

PROFESSIONAL EMAIL

* Create custom email addresses (e.g., you@yourbrand.com).
* Account Limits: (Launch: 2, Grow: 4, Pro: 8) Email accounts are included.
* Accessible via Webmail or connectable to Gmail/Outlook/iPhone.
* The number of accounts scales with your plan.

